Package org.apache.daffodil.japi.infoset

Class InfosetOutputter

java.lang.Object
org.apache.daffodil.japi.infoset.InfosetOutputter
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.apache.daffodil.runtime1.infoset.BlobMethodsMixin, org.apache.daffodil.runtime1.infoset.InfosetOutputter
Direct Known Subclasses:
InfosetOutputterProxy
public abstract class InfosetOutputter extends Object implements org.apache.daffodil.runtime1.infoset.InfosetOutputter
Abstract class used to determine how the infoset representation should be output from a call to DataProcessor#parse. The Daffodil core will call the various methods of this class in an order appropriate to create an infoset representation.

Classes that extend InfosetOutputter are not guaranteed to be thread-safe.
